"Yes, but I had another idea about that," Zorian said.
 "What if… we recruited his help in breaking into the Eldemar's royal vault?"

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Zach gave him a surprised look.

\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
"That's a pretty interesting idea, but how would we possibly divide the
 spoils?" Zach asked.
 "I mean, both sides will want to claim the dagger in the end…"

